hopobject.body: Do you know what extension he's on? medicinediscounts.xyz "I have conferred with the chairmen of the national security committees who have received initial outreach from senior administration officials, and while the outreach has been appreciated, it is apparent [it] has, to date, not reached the level of substantive consultation," said House Speaker John Boehner in a letter sent to Obama Wednesday. He asked the president to "fully make the case" for intervention to both the American public and Congress.
